# 📊 Power BI & Excel Sales Analytics Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview

An end-to-end data analytics project featuring two interactive dashboards built with **Power BI** and **Excel**, 
analyzing sales and profit performance across multiple dimensions — country, product category, time, and region.

| Dashboard | Tool | Dataset |
|---|---|---|
| Super Store Profit & Revenue Analysis | Power BI | Superstore Dataset |
| Bike Sales Performance Analysis | Excel | Bike Sales Dataset |

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Analyze revenue and profit trends across countries and product categories
- Identify top-performing regions, products, and time periods
- Deliver interactive, executive-ready dashboards for data-driven decisions
- Demonstrate proficiency in Power BI, DAX, Excel, and data visualization

---

