## 🖼️ Dashboard Previews

### Power BI — Super Store Profit & Revenue Analysis

![Power BI Dashboard](Screenshot%20(1).png)

**Key KPIs:**

| Metric | Value |
|---|---|
| Total Revenue | $85M |
| Total Profit | $32M |
| Order Quantity | 1M |
| Profit Margin | 37.8% |

**Features:**
- Profit breakdown by Country, State, Sub-Category & Product Category
- Time-based revenue and profit trend analysis
- Interactive slicers for year and region filtering
- Dynamic tooltips for deeper on-hover insights

---

### Excel — Bike Sales Performance Analysis

**Key KPIs:**
- Revenue trends by product and region
- Profitability analysis by category
- Seasonal sales patterns and year-over-year comparison
- Slicer-enabled filters for year, product, and location

---

## 💡 Key Business Insights

- 📈 **Revenue Growth** — Consistent upward trend identified across key markets from 2011 to 2016
- 🌍 **Market Leadership** — USA leads all countries in total profit contribution at $11M
- 🚲 **Product Dominance** — Bikes account for ~64% of total profit, making them the core revenue driver
- 🛒 **Category Performance** — Accessories and Clothing contribute supporting revenue streams worth investing in
- 📅 **Seasonal Patterns** — Excel dashboard reveals peak sales periods and slow seasons for strategic inventory planning

